surf_insanity_light

This version of insanity is a fix from the original surf_insanity.

I fixed...
- Lightmap scale
- Skybox
- Ammo for deagles
- The map size has been scaled down to 11.4 mb!!
- You do not have to have sv_downloadurl to distribute

Thanks to SintaxError with helping me on the Lightmaps. Visit his forums @ http://forums.solidsurf.info/

Enjoy!
